Chicken and veggie stir-fry
20 | Main dish
chicken breast	450
broccoli	250
mushroom	225
oil	3
garlic	3
soy sauce	2
In a large pan on medium-high heat, add 1 tablespoon of oil. Once the oil is hot, add chicken, season with salt and pepper, and sauté until cooked through and browned. Remove cooked chicken from pan and set aside. Add 1 tablespoon of oil to the pan and sauté garlic and ginger until fragrant. Add the remaining sauce ingredients and stir until smooth.